nodes.text: An unidentified Valorum was a member of the Valorum family of Coruscant, and served as Supreme Chancellor, some time prior to 62 BBY.

In Darth Plagueis, Palpatine remembered that "(Finis Valorum's) election to the chancellorship had more to do with a pedigree that included three Supreme Chancellors (Tarsus Valorum, Eixes Valorum and an unidentified individual) and deals he had cut with infuential families like the Kalpanas and the Tarkins of Eriadu."
